	* tools/tiffcrop.c: Fix some portability problems.

	* libtiff/tif_ojpeg.c: Use same jpeg/win32 boolean/FAR hacks as are
	used in tif_jpeg.c.

	* libtiff/tif_win32.c: Ensure TIFFOpenW() uses same FILE_SHARE flags
	as TIFFOpen().

